    "body": "## Steps to reproduce\r\n1. Add at least one page as a shortcut to the device's homescreen.\r\n2. Close Focus.\r\n3. Open the shortcut from the homescreen.\r\n4. Go to Settings - General - Language, and select a different language.\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\nThe selected language is applied without issues.\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\nThe selected language is applied, but the shortcut is opened in a new tab - please see the short video below.\r\n\r\n### Device information\r\n* Android device: Lenovo Tab M10 (Android 10)\r\n* Focus version: Beta 100.0.0-beta.1, Focus Nightly 100.0a1 from 4/5\r\n\r\n[logcat.txt](https://github.com/mozilla-mobile/focus-android/files/8415987/logcat.txt)\r\n\r\nhttps://user-images.githubusercontent.com/40694158/161704086-9f0513ec-60d2-4df3-a8c1-a9eb8104a8aa.mp4\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
